abstract: Florida State athletic director Stan Wilcox says university will investigate statement made by former quarterback Jameis Winston in connection with shoplifting incident.
lead_paragraph: Florida State Athletic Director Stan Wilcox said the university would investigate the statement by the former Seminoles quarterback Jameis Winston.

headline.main: F.S.U. to Examine Jameis Winston Comments

snippet: Florida State Athletic Director Stan Wilcox said the university would investigate the statement by the former Seminoles quarterback Jameis Winston.
